# Generated by `kf docs` (rendered ```kf``` blocks); dodeca builds this.
docs/.rendered/
# NOTE: docs/static/kf-fonts.css is generated by `kf docs` too, but must NOT be
# gitignored — dodeca's static walker respects .gitignore, so an ignored file
# is never served (404). It's regenerated on every `kf docs` run; commit it (a
# stable asset that only changes when the engraving fonts do) or leave untracked.

